		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Something video game animators never got right was punching animation.  Too many games had fists popping out of nowhere.  Sure it lets you attack your opponents faster, but it also gives you no twitch time to respond from your opponent before his fist appears out of nowhere.

		

